_sText:
This is a very simple Deathrun map with 3 floors, it doesn't contain a lot traps - but I think it's enough and if it aint, just tell me and I'll upgrade it. I'll love to get feedback, both positive and negative, so just post a comment below.

The map contains:
- 9 Traps(Controlled by T)
- 2 Random Traps
- 51 CT Spawns
- 11 T Spawns
- 2 Secrets
- a MP5 at the end with colors, for the first person to end the track

This is just a Beta, in the future I'll finish the final version which should be; Longer, different texture, more secrets and more/funnier endings.
Thank you.
